Campaign - Single or Two-Player, main story mode. Hero class and Horror boss available.
Skirmish - Singleplayer, choose a pre-set fight and select your team. Only classes available.
Versus - Two-Player, compete against another player. Classes and monsters available.
Challenge - Singleplayer, run pre-set gauntlets with predetermined teams. Classes and monsters available. Challenges unlock from achievements.
Conquest - Singleplayer, evil campaign unlocked after beating Campaign.
